description:
In this episode, we continue to learn about the evolution of the Seventh Day Adventist Church and the Sabbath. Rachel Oakes was a Seventh Day Bapist and felt strongly about following God. She confronted Frederick Wheeler after communion, telling him that he should follow God all the way. How do you respond when something you are doing is pointed as being wrong? Frederick had to grapple with this question after an encounter with Rachel Preston in Washington, NH that would change the course of his life and ministry.

To find out more information about Frederick Wheeler and Rachel Oakes Preston read our extended article on our website. 

https://lineagejourney.com/read/frederick-wheeler-and-rachel-oakes/
